unpublishedAction.name: initializeRetainKPObject

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
        const retain_keyPersonData = {}
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ENTITY_TYPE = 'Key Person Foreign'
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TYPE = vayKeyPersonFgnType.selectedOptionValue
				//showAlert('Key Person Tyep'+ retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TYPE)
			  retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_IS_AUTH_SIGN = vayisMinor.isChecked
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_OTHERS_INFO = vaypartnerperct.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PARTNER_PERC = vayOwnershipPerct.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FIRSTNAME = vayDesignationOthers.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MIDDLENAME = vayDinDpin.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_LASTNAME = vayFname.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOTHERNAME = vayMName.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FATHERNAME = vayLname.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DOB = moment(vayIndDOB.selectedDate).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TAX_ID = Input7.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_NATIONALITY = Select3.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_RES_TAX_PURPOSE = Select4.selectedOptionValue
        //retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DESIGNATION  = ''
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_NO = Input21.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_EXPIRE_DATE = moment(vayIndDOB.selectedDate).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ACCESS_AS = vayKeyPersonFgnUserAccess.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DIN_DPIN = Input8.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE1 = vayIndAddrLin1.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE2 = vayIndAddrLin2.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY = vayIndCityLocality.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_DISTRICT = vayIndCityDistrict.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE = vayIndStateCountry.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY = vayFgnKeyPersonAddCountrySelec.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_ZIP = Input15.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOBILE = vayPassportNo.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_EMAIL = vayGovtIssueId.text
        appsmith.store.vayCCY.map((item) => {
            return ({
                CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_CODE_FORADMTXN: item,
                CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_LIMIT: vayIndCKYCNO.text
            });
        });
        return retain_keyPersonData
    }
